    "date": "2009-03-06T20:12:08Z",
    "text": "Senior Assets Verification Exemption (SAVE) from Capital Gains Tax Act of 2009 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow a tax deduction for the qualified net capital gain of taxpayers age 65 and older. Defines \"qualified net capital gain\" as the lesser of: (1) net capital gain; or (2) net capital gain only from assets held for at least 15 years."
